<div class="scroll">
	<div class="scroll__text">
		<div class="step">
			<p>Here is the New York City region, an area of 18 million people. Each dot represents 1,000 square. meters. Dots with a deeper shade of <span class="red">red</span> represent more people.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="step" id="tilt-shift-step">
			<p>But there’s another way to look at population. Let's grow each dot into a 3D block.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="step" id="rotate-step">
			<p>Taller blocks also represent more people, and you can start to see a city's population as a mountainous terrain.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
